[
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "那小丐",
    "listener": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "text": "饱了，不吃了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 42,
    "line_end": 42
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "那小丐",
    "listener": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "text": "你没钱，我有钱，请你吃几个馒头，打什么紧？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 56,
    "line_end": 56
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "那小丐",
    "listener": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "text": "什么叫讲义气？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 68,
    "line_end": 68
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "speaker_name": "谢烟客",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "我怎么不讲义气？我当然讲义气。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 73,
    "line_end": 73
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "那小丐",
    "listener": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "text": "我知道啦，做好事的是好人，做坏事的是坏人，你老是做好事，因此是个大大的好人。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 74,
    "line_end": 74
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "那小丐",
    "listener": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "text": "这是黑衣相公的。黑衣相公和观音娘娘做一道，我也不能要他的东西。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 60,
    "line_end": 60
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "speaker_name": "谢烟客",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "狗杂种，你倒挺讲义气哪。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 68,
    "line_end": 68
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "那少年",
    "listener": "char_shi_jian",
    "text": "侍剑姊姊，我到底是谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_jian",
    "speaker_name": "侍剑",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "你是长乐帮的帮主，姓石，名字叫破天。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 16,
    "line_end": 16
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": "char_shi_jian",
    "text": "长乐帮是什么东西？帮主是干什么的？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 22,
    "line_end": 22
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": "char_chen_chong_zhi",
    "text": "陈……陈香主也大好了，我也向你问安。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 48,
    "line_end": 48
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": "char_shi_jian",
    "text": "糊的也好吃，怕什么？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 72,
    "line_end": 72
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": "char_shi_jian",
    "text": "你见到我妈妈没有？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 82,
    "line_end": 82
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
    "speaker_name": "史婆婆",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "我老婆子收你做徒弟，你磕不磕头？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
    "text": "我师父是长乐帮的贝先生，不能另外拜师了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 28,
    "line_end": 28
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
    "speaker_name": "丁珰",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "天哥，你想不想我？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 18,
    "line_end": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
    "speaker_name": "丁珰",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "好啊，你不想我，是不是？你只想着那个新和你拜天地的新娘子。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 20,
    "line_end": 20
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
    "speaker_name": "丁珰",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "菩萨保佑，但愿你永生永世再也找不着她。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 30,
    "line_end": 30
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": "char_ding_dang",
    "text": "叮叮当当，你好不好？那天我给你抛到江中，幸好掉在一艘船上，才没淹死。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 35,
    "line_end": 35
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
    "speaker_name": "丁珰",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "什么幸好掉在一艘船上？是我故意抛你上去的，难道你不知道？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 38,
    "line_end": 38
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
    "speaker_name": "丁珰",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "天哥，你老实跟我说，是我好看呢？还是你那个新的老婆好看？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 52,
    "line_end": 52
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": "char_ding_dang",
    "text": "叮叮当当，你……你真好看，比我妈妈还好看。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 70,
    "line_end": 70
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": "char_shi_qing",
    "text": "我……我到底是谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 52,
    "line_end": 52
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_min_rou",
    "speaker_name": "闵柔",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "孩儿，你不用害怕，你那次发烧挺厉害，把从前的事都烧得忘记啦，慢慢的就会记起来。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 60,
    "line_end": 60
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": "char_min_rou",
    "text": "妈妈！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 80,
    "line_end": 80
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_min_rou",
    "speaker_name": "闵柔",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "好孩儿，乖儿子！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 81,
    "line_end": 81
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_min_rou",
    "speaker_name": "闵柔",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "如来佛保佑，佑护我儿疾病早愈。他小时无知，干下的罪孽，都由为娘的一身抵挡，一切责罚，都由为娘的来承受。千刀万剐，甘受不辞，只求我儿今后重新做人，一生无灾无难，平安喜乐。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 95,
    "line_end": 95
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "speaker_name": "谢烟客",
    "listener": "char_shi_zhong_yu",
    "text": "狗杂种，原来是你。",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_zhong_yu",
    "speaker_name": "石中玉",
    "listener": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "text": "原来是谢先生。",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 18,
    "line_end": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "speaker_name": "谢烟客",
    "listener": "char_shi_zhong_yu",
    "text": "很好，很好！你这小子居然当上了长乐帮帮主！",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 20,
    "line_end": 20
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "speaker_name": "谢烟客",
    "listener": "char_shi_zhong_yu",
    "text": "好罢，是你从我手中接过玄铁令的，你要我为你办什么事，快快说来。谢某一生纵横江湖，便遇上天大难事，也视作等闲。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 55,
    "line_end": 55
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_zhong_yu",
    "speaker_name": "石中玉",
    "listener": "char_xie_yan_ke",
    "text": "在下斗胆，请谢先生到凌霄城去，将雪山派人众尽数杀了。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 68,
    "line_end": 68
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_bei_hai_shi",
    "speaker_name": "贝海石",
    "listener": "char_shi_zhong_yu",
    "text": "帮……帮主，一……一……路保重，恕……恕……属下……咳咳……不送了！",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 80,
    "line_end": 80
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_feng_wan_li",
    "speaker_name": "封万里",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "刚才有人大声叱喝，要将长门一支的弟子尽数杀了，不知是谁放的狗屁？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 48,
    "line_end": 48
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhang_san",
    "speaker_name": "张三",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我倒有个主意在此。你们五位以武功决胜败，谁的功夫最强，谁便是雪山派掌门。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 55,
    "line_end": 55
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
    "speaker_name": "史婆婆",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "进去罢！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 62,
    "line_end": 62
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
    "speaker_name": "史婆婆",
    "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "text": "若有一线生机，你千万要自行脱逃，不能为了相救爷爷而自陷绝地。此是为师的严令，决不可违。",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
    "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "众位心中尚有什么疑窦，便请直言。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 18,
    "line_end": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
    "speaker_name": "白自在",
    "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
    "text": "龙岛主说是邀我们来看古诗图解，那到底是什么东西，便请赐观如何？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 20,
    "line_end": 20
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
    "speaker_name": "丁不四",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "一切都是随意，可客气得很啊。就是不能'随意离岛'，是不是？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 35,
    "line_end": 35
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
    "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "丁先生何出此言？各位来到侠客岛是出于自愿，若要离去，又有谁敢强留？海滩边大船小船一应俱全，各位何时意欲归去，尽可自便。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 38,
    "line_end": 38
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
    "speaker_name": "石破天",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "糟糕，糟糕！爷爷，今……今天是几……几月初……初几啊？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 8,
    "line_end": 8
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
    "speaker_name": "白自在",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "苦也，苦也！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 22,
    "line_end": 22
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
    "speaker_name": "丁不四",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "甜也，甜也！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 24,
    "line_end": 24
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
    "speaker_name": "丁不四",
    "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
    "text": "白自在，他妈的你这老畜生，你……你为什么不早早回去？你这狗养的老贼！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 30,
    "line_end": 30
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
    "speaker_name": "白自在",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不错，我是老混蛋，我是老贼。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 32,
    "line_end": 32
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mei_wen_xin",
    "speaker_name": "梅文馨",
    "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
    "text": "你只盼我早已死了，这才快活，是不是？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 85,
    "line_end": 85
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
    "speaker_name": "丁不四",
    "listener": "char_mei_wen_xin",
    "text": "快放手！众英雄在此，有什么好看？",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 88,
    "line_end": 88
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mei_wen_xin",
    "speaker_name": "梅文馨",
    "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
    "text": "我的芳姑呢？还我来！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 90,
    "line_end": 90
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shi_qing",
    "speaker_name": "石清",
    "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
    "text": "白老伯有所不知，这个梅芳姑，便是侄儿夫妇的杀子大仇人。我们东打听，西寻访，在江湖上找了她一十八年，得不到半点音讯。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 65,
    "line_end": 65
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
    "speaker_name": "白自在",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这女子杀死了你们的儿子？岂有此理，不错，非去将她碎尸万段不可。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 68,
    "line_end": 68
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
    "speaker_name": "白自在",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你管他两个二月也好，有三个二月也好，只要老婆没死，师父没死，便有一百个二月也不相干！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 55,
    "line_end": 55
  }
]